snippet.title: Virtual Battlegrounds - Launch Trailer | Eye of the Storm
snippet.description:
Virtual Battlegrounds is the ultimate Battle Royale being built from the ground up for virtual reality.  Battle to become the last man standing on this apocalyptic war-crazed island through tactical gun-play, an epic map, and physical based controls for skydiving, climbing, shooting, ziplining, and driving.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/cyberdreamvr
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CyberDreamVR/
Discord: https://discord.gg/jsyWfcS

Add Virtual Battlegrounds to your wishlist:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/823940/Virtual_Battlegrounds/

Purchase the song Eye of the Storm: 
https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/eye-of-the-storm-single/1221133063
